{
    "_readme": [
        "Canonical locale spec for the Vacademy monorepo — the single source of truth",
        "for supported locales, their order, RTL membership, default locale, native",
        "labels and scripts. Each frontend app carries a generated mirror at",
        "src/i18n/locales.ts (frontend-admin-dashboard, frontend-learner-dashboard-app)",
        "that MUST match this file. Never hand-edit those mirrors: change this file,",
        "then run `node scripts/gen-locales.mjs` to regenerate them (the per-app",
        "RTL_READY flag is preserved across regenerations). Locale codes are BCP-47."
    ],
    "supported": ["en", "ar", "hi", "ta", "te", "bn", "mr", "gu", "kn", "ml", "pa", "or", "as", "es", "fr"],
